    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-1a' );" name="003-1a" class="pb">[003-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　毛詩名物解卷三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:220'>　　　　　　　　　　宋　蔡　卞　集解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:226'>　釋百榖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='226:247'>　　　黍　　稷　　稻　　粱　　禾　　麻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='247:268'>　　　菽　　麥　　牟　　稗　　稙　　穉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='268:289'>　　　穜　　秬　　秠　　穈　　芑　　苴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='289:294'>　　黍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='294:320'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-1b' );" name="003-1b" class="pb">[003-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='320:343'>黍丹榖也仲夏乃登故謂之黍而聲與暑同氣浮而味</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='343:366'>甘馨香而滑齊故宜釀神陽物也非有馨香上逹之氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='366:389'>不足以降之黍陽物也故用為酒釀凡言黍稷者皆有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='389:402'>冀祖考懷祭祀念父母之意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='402:407'>　　稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='407:430'>稷祭也所以祭故謂之穄杜預言黍稷曰粢降食以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='430:453'>酒貴食次之故穄者粱也所以祭明尊矣故五榖之官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='453:460'>而稷官名之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='460:486'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-2a' );" name="003-2a" class="pb">[003-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='486:491'>　　稻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='491:514'>稻稌也豐年曰豐年多黍多稌蓋黍所以交神稌所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='514:536'>養人先王之盛時和而歳豐交鬼神養人之物備矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='536:541'>　　粱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='541:564'>天以始至甘香者也粱從米所以濟人者也從刃所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='564:587'>利人者也豐年言養人之物而不言粱者蓋稌加膳於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='587:594'>粱則為嘗膳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='594:599'>　　禾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='599:625'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-2b' );" name="003-2b" class="pb">[003-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='625:649'>禾粟之苖榦粟禾之穟實春秋者隂陽之中粟春生而秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='649:673'>熟方其以養生言之則謂之禾禾麻菽麥禾役穟穟是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='673:696'>方其以所用言之則謂之粟率場啄粟握粟出卜是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='696:701'>　　麻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='701:724'>麻八榖之良者也實謂苴從且榖之貴者人可以爲食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='724:747'>而不可以爲常也七月言九月菽苴采荼薪樗此先王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='747:770'>所以致食而勞農之意也五榖之養人以浮虚爲下以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='770:793'>沉實爲上胡麻之食沉實者也故良以敬人稷者交神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='793:819'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-3a' );" name="003-3a" class="pb">[003-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='819:842'>之至實者也凡榖之至貴者又宜加碓以治之麻從林</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='842:865'>稷從畟皆勤治之意也麻爲麻枲之麻者以其求治析</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='865:876'>治於覆屋之下故同字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='876:881'>　　菽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='881:904'>菽謂之荏菽祀天地蓋菽有收斂之意而亦人所先也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='904:927'>稻粱加膳也粟菽常膳也君子制而不爲異亦蹈其常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='927:950'>而已故菽亦謂喻君子之徳中原有菽庶民采之言徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='950:980'>足以養人者天下之所歸<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0616' title='KR0616' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0616.png'/>也采菽采菽筐之莒之言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='980:1006'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-3b' );" name="003-3b" class="pb">[003-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1006:1017'>取有徳受之以法度也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1017:1022'>　　麥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1022:1045'>麥之同乎陽者也至子而苖至午而成陽多則浮隂多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1045:1068'>則沉隂陽不相勝然後能善養人者也故麥可以爲美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1068:1077'>而不可爲加膳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1077:1082'>　　牟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1082:1105'>牟可以爲助膳而非膳也牟麥之大者也先禾而生後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1105:1128'>禾而熟以其大故爲五榖之長麥之異種思文言貽我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1128:1154'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-4a' );" name="003-4a" class="pb">[003-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1154:1177'>來牟后稷種藝以粒民者多矣來牟民先得以爲利者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1177:1180'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1180:1199'>　　稗　稙　穉　穜　秬　秠　穈　芑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1199:1222'>稗可以食而非凶荒則不食冝小人而使之困也先種</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1222:1245'>謂之稙後種謂之穉先熟謂之稑後熟謂之穜黑黍謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1245:1268'>之秬二米謂之秠赤粱謂之穈白粱謂之芑稙直逹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1268:1291'>故爲先種穉有待也故爲後種稑以言其和於土而苖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1291:1314'>遂之於蚤也故爲先熟穜以言其晚成而多實也故爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1314:1340'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-4b' );" name="003-4b" class="pb">[003-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1340:1363'>後熟秬齊正而有才者也故麻之實八角而純黑者謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1363:1386'>之秬律度量衡以秬準之者以其方正滑齊而可用也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1386:1409'>秠不一也故爲一稃而二米穈者良之又良者也受成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1409:1432'>於火故其色赤芑者榖之至善者也受成於金故其色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1432:1455'>白萬物豐於火成於金穈有豐實之性也芑有成實之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1455:1478'>性蓋稙穉以言其榖之備穜稑以言其榖之美秬秠穈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1478:1501'>芑以言其榖之嘉也七月陳先公風化之所由得土之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1501:1524'>盛故曰穜稑稙穉之種因天時也穜稑之實得地氣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1524:1550'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-5a' );" name="003-5a" class="pb">[003-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1550:1573'>閟宫備言后稷稼穡之道故校四者而言之爲稼穡而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1573:1596'>因天時得地氣此所以降之百福也美榖可以養人嘉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1596:1619'>榖不可以爲食之常也先王用之於祭祀而已故生民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1619:1637'>言后稷之肈祀而曰誕降嘉榖秬秠穈芑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1637:1642'>　　苴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1642:1665'>苴所謂婦雀以苴之者已則棄焉所謂苴履者安可長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1665:1688'>也所謂棲苴者道者而已非所以爲存所謂土苴者此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1688:1708'>也所謂菽苴者其爲榖苴而已故六榖弗數焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1708:1734'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '003-5b' );" name="003-5b" class="pb">[003-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
